alace spain\" class=\"wp-image-88974 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1312px) 100vw, 1312px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165117\/alhambra-granada-spain-15.jpg 1312w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165117\/alhambra-granada-spain-15-410x600.jpg 410w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165117\/alhambra-granada-spain-15-554x810.jpg 554w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165117\/alhambra-granada-spain-15-231x338.jpg 231w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165117\/alhambra-granada-spain-15-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165117\/alhambra-granada-spain-15-111x163.jpg 111w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165117\/alhambra-granada-spain-15-123x180.jpg 123w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165117\/alhambra-granada-spain-15-525x768.jpg 525w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165117\/alhambra-granada-spain-15-700x1024.jpg 700w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165117\/alhambra-granada-spain-15-738x1080.jpg 738w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165117\/alhambra-granada-spain-15-984x1440.jpg 984w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165117\/alhambra-granada-spain-15-300x439.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165117\/alhambra-granada-spain-15-600x878.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165117\/alhambra-granada-spain-15-150x220.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165117\/alhambra-granada-spain-15-21x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165117\/alhambra-granada-spain-15.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Every detail is breathtaking: the stonework carved into the most beautiful patterns and even the heavy wooden tours carved with beautiful Islamic-style details. It&#x2019;s hard to believe you&#x2019;re in Spain and not in a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/morocco\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Moroccan<\/a> palace!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102846\/granada-spain-7.jpg\" alt=\" alhambra palace granada spain\"><\/noscript><img width=\"253\" height=\"338\" alt=\" alhambra palace granada spain\" class=\"wp-image-86859 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1438px) 100vw, 1438px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102846\/granada-spain-7.jpg 1438w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102846\/granada-spain-7-449x600.jpg 449w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102846\/granada-spain-7-607x810.jpg 607w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102846\/granada-spain-7-253x338.jpg 253w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102846\/granada-spain-7-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03102846\/granada-spain-7-122x163.jpg 12