ntainer\">\n<h3 id=\"h-generalife\">Generalife<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Generalife houses the incredible gardens of Alhambra, with its lovely walkways, fountains, beautiful hedgerows, and giant ancient trees. In the spring\/summer, the gardens really come to life when the flowers and rose gardens burst into bloom. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04120234\/granada-spain-24.jpg\" alt=\"Generalife alhambra granada spain\"><\/noscript><img width=\"222\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Generalife alhambra granada spain\" class=\"wp-image-86924 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1263px) 100vw, 1263px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04120234\/granada-spain-24.jpg 1263w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04120234\/granada-spain-24-395x600.jpg 395w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04120234\/granada-spain-24-533x810.jpg 533w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04120234\/granada-spain-24-222x338.jpg 222w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04120234\/granada-spain-24-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04120234\/granada-spain-24-107x163.jpg 107w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04120234\/granada-spain-24-118x180.jpg 118w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04120234\/granada-spain-24-505x768.jpg 505w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04120234\/granada-spain-24-674x1024.jpg 674w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04120234\/granada-spain-24-710x1080.jpg 710w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04120234\/granada-spain-24-947x1440.jpg 947w,