v class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>If you miss your slot time, you&#x2019;ll sadly lose your entrance to the palaces. This is one of the most beautiful parts of the Royal Alhambra Palace, so make sure to keep an eye on the time.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip: <\/strong>You have to show your ticket for entry into each section of Alhambra, so keep your Alhambra tickets somewhere safe.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165053\/alhambra-granada-spain-14.jpg\" alt=\"alhambra granada things to do spain\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"alhambra granada things to do spain\" class=\"wp-image-88972 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165053\/alhambra-granada-spain-14.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165053\/alhambra-granada-spain-14-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165053\/alhambra-granada-spain-14-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165053\/alhambra-granada-spain-14-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/29165053\/alhambra-granada-spain-14-20x30.jpg 20w, http