/a> cost 14 EUR (15 USD) for a self-guided tour and must be pre-booked online before arrival. As Alhambra is the most visited site in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/spain\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Spain<\/a>, it&#x2019;s best to book well in advance to avoid disappointment (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/alhambra-ticket\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Alhambra tickets<\/a> are available up to 90 days before). An audio guide is included in the price, so you can learn about Alhambra as you go.&#xA0;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n                <div data-gyg-href=\"https:\/\/widget.getyourguide.com\/default\/activities.frame\" data-gyg-locale-code=\"en-US\" data-gyg-widget=\"activities\" data-gyg-number-of-items=\"3\" data-gyg-tour-ids=\"71958,397263,397264\" data-gyg-partner-id=\"SYAMOP2\" data-gyg-cmp=\"alhambra-widget\" class=\"lazyload block-getyourguide\" data-script=\"https:\/\/widget.getyourguide.com\/dist\/pa.umd.production.min.js\"><\/div>\n            \n\n\n<p>Alternatively, join a tour if you want insider knowledge about Alhambra Palace. This is also an easy way to buy your tickets and skip the line. However, be aware that the big group tours do move through the complex quite fast. For a more unique, intimate experience, we recommend a private tour.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-alhambra-opening-times\">Alhambra Opening Times<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Alhambra is open every day apart from Christmas and the first of January.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4><strong>April 01 &#x2013; October 14&#xA0;<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Opening times through the spring\/summer are 8.30 AM &#x2013; 8 PM. Alhambra closes at 8 PM, so make sure to enter at least a few hours before.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>During these months, it&#x2019;s also possible to do a night tour from Tuesday to Saturday.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4><strong>October 15 &#x2013; March 31<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Opening times in the winter months are 8.30 AM &#x2013; 6 PM. During this period, evening visits are limited to Friday and Saturday only.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/granada-hotels\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Granada.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04114520\/granada-spain-8.jpg\" alt=\"alhambra granada door\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"alhambra granada door\" class=\"wp-image-86918 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04114520\/granada-spain-8.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04114520\/granada-spain-8-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04114520\/granada-spain-8-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04114520\/granada-spain-8-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04114520\/granada-spain-8-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/04114520\/granada-spain-8-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-conten