\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-getting-to-granada\">Getting to Granada<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Granada has a small airport that serves major cities in Spain, like <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/spain\/barcelona-travel-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Barcelona<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/spain\/things-to-do-madrid\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Madrid<\/a>. There are also some flights from major cities, like London, but these are very infrequent and often seasonal. For this reason, it&#x2019;s best to fly to the international airport of Malaga.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--flight \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--flight\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/flights-malaga\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your flight to Malaga<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granada-spain-12.jpg\" alt=\"Catedral de granada\"><\/noscript><img width=\"239\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Catedral de granada\" class=\"wp-image-86864 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1356px) 100vw, 1356px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granada-spain-12.jpg 1356w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granada-spain-12-424x600.jpg 424w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/03104540\/granad