D;n is the best neighborhood to stay in if you want views of the Alhambra. This beautiful old part of the city is on a higher level than the city center and has many viewpoints where you can look out onto the palace. As it&#x2019;s a local area, most accommodations here are self-catering apartments.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02154636\/granada-spain-10.jpg\" alt=\"things to do granada spain Albaic&#xED;n Neighborhood\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do granada spain Albaic&#xED;n Neighborhood\" class=\"wp-image-86846 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02154636\/granada-spain-10.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02154636\/granada-spain-10-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02154636\/granada-spain-10-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02154636\/granada-spain-10-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02154636\/granada-spain-10-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02154636\/granada-spain-10-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02154636\/granada-spain-10-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02154636\/granada-spain-10-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02154636\/granada-spain-10-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02154636\/granada-spain-10-835x1080.jpg 835w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/021546